<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA89">
<l>oḷivi livaṉmataṉai yoṇpoṭiyā nōkkit</l>
<l>teḷivuḷḷa cintaiyiṉiṟ cērvā - yoḷinañca</l>
<l>muṇṭavā yaḵtiruppa vuṉṉuṭaiya kaṇṭamiruṭ</l>
<l>koṇṭavā ṟeṉṉitaṉaik kūṟu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You, who, looking strong Mataṉ, who was without hiding place, to be bright ash,</l>
<l>join in thoughts that are clear, tell me this: what is the way</l>
<l>your throat takes darkness while that is the mouth</l>
<l>that has eaten the bright poison?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
